(13473, 'Rosulipid 10 mg 10 tabs', 'روزيوليبيد 10 مجم 10 اقراص', '', '36', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Company', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antihyperlipidemic.statins', '10 mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
